Body: Description: Same issue when we upgrade to 11.5 in case 00411545. Tried the steps from that case here, but didn't seem to correct it. Under version 11.5 (previously 11), we had an analysis created for our AD user summary (for licensing), but it seems to have disappeared in the GUI since our upgrade to 11.6. I see C:Program Files (x86)STEALTHbitsStealthAUDITJobsGROUP_.Active Directory InventoryJOB_1-AD_ScanVIEW_SA_ADInventoryWLGORE_LicenseUsers.INI.xml still exists in the files, but not sure how to import or recreate it in StealthAudit?
Steps to Reproduce Updated: Performing a Full Upgrade of the AD Solutions.
